secondary_outcome.description:
Will be assessed on a 7-point ordinal scale. The scale is as follows:
Death;
Hospitalized, on invasive mechanical ventilation or ECMO;
Hospitalized, on non-invasive ventilation or high flow oxygen devices;
Hospitalized, requiring low flow supplemental oxygen;
Hospitalized, not requiring supplemental oxygen - requiring ongoing medical care (COVID-19 related or otherwise);
Hospitalized, not requiring supplemental oxygen - no longer requires ongoing medical care (other than per protocol RDV administration);
Not hospitalized
